            "text": "Tool Chaining \u2014 'get_server_health' directs LLM to call monitor_legislative_pipeline. Tool 'get_server_health' description references tool(s) 'monitor_legislative_pipeline' from the same server using imperative language. This pattern can force an LLM into an unintended call chain or manufacture urgency to invoke a privileged tool."
          },
          "locations": [
